			<h1>Primary Care Depression Guidelines and Treatment Resistant Depression: Variations on an Important but Understudied Theme</h1>
			<p class="byline">By: Bradley N. Gaynes, MD, MPH, Linda J. Lux, MPA, and Gerald Gartlehner, MD, MPH</p>
		</div><!-- /.content-header-meta -->

		<!-- TOOLBAR -->
